An shape is an thing with
  an kind [arc, ellipse, group, picture, polygon, rectangle, text],
  an box,
  an selected flag, an previously selected flag,
  an scale ratio,
  an border color and an fill color,
  an ellipse [ellipse],
  an picture [picture],
  an polygon [polygon],
  an rect [rectangle],
  an text rect, an label, and an text [text],
  some shapes [group].
  
  